{"tid":2181440,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"★ 42萬人登記檢測　過半中心周二額滿","createTime":"2020-08-30T15:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T15:19:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4072f5b71402377a052ca4292ebc2b4e7cf1c84","tid":2181440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】普及社區檢測截至下午6時，共42萬人登記預約。計劃開展首天有80個中心爆滿，政府指會考慮會否將計劃延長最多七日。另外，政府收到至少8宗投訴，懷疑被盜用個人資料來預約，3宗已交由警方跟進，亦已取消預約。<br />\n<br />\n普及社區檢測開放網上預約第二日，截至下午六時，全港141個檢測中心，有80個檢測首日，即星期二已滿額，包括荃灣區三個中心，而離島區唯一的採樣中心東涌文東路體育館，七天有五天都已滿額。另外，五個檢測中心，七天都已爆滿。政府呼籲考慮預約其他中心，又指會密切監察情況，考慮會否將計劃延長最多七日。<br />\n<br />\n政府收到8宗投訴，涉嫌盜用他人的資料預約，當中三宗已交警方處理。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒：「有朋友通知我們，他們的資料被人用作登記，我想強調，盜用他人個人資料屬違法行為，如果我們一經確認有這些違法行為，我們會轉交警方跟進。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，有網民用虛構的身份證號碼及名字都成功登記，被質疑登記數字可造假。薛永恒稱計劃為了便民，需要填的資料都相對簡單。<br />\n<br />\n薛永恒：「如果登記人未能填上清楚的身份證號碼，其實是辦不到的，因為有方法確保填上身份證屬真確。」<br />\n<br />\n政府後來發新聞稿補充，檢測計劃下，已取消的登記不會計入登記紀錄，絕無「篤數」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=403551&amp;hot=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403551%26hot%3D1&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=bde2f816\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fhot%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403551%26hot%3D1&h=85a05d7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/hot/player?newsId=403551&amp;hot=1</a>"},{"pid":"82c6534b22879af0888659cee6f61f440c93edeb","tid":2181440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5c797c1ba67402440f07ffa7fe3ceeb4023e28","tid":2181440,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"老貓星期二係咪會開 youtube live 直播檢測？"},{"pid":"fb18243a9117fade53ab2cfa7554c1402a8cdb9d","tid":2181440,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"有幾多被自願<br />\n根本唔會跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ec5e03eee747a1b874644ce0a9485c0a3fb231","tid":2181440,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:10:58.000Z","msg":"老貓一定有登記"},{"pid":"eaae3bd4a770daaa05345fd9f6eea50749d721bd","tid":2181440,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5c797c1ba67402440f07ffa7fe3ceeb4023e28","tid":2181440,"uid":85168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:06:07.000Z","msg":"老貓星期二係咪會開 youtube live 直播檢測？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"似<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AaD9Tsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAaD9Tsg.jpg&h=99d02812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef951ed72ae35739f2329fc1196d0e9c18bf8291","tid":2181440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"正版<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmcUCvU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmcUCvU.png&h=65508e61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59b0bc8be3d977ed3bd54215bb2726e5873299bf","tid":2181440,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FmcUCvU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFmcUCvU.png&h=65508e61&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}